    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Acute\npain\n, swelling, and mild tooth elevation\nExquisite sensitivity to percussion or chewing on the involved tooth\nSwelling in surrounding gingiva, buccal, lingual or palatal regions\nMay see small white pustule (parulis) in gingival surface characteristic for abscesses",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": [
        {
          "text": "pain",
          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/Dental_pain"
        }
      ]
